A frustrated man sits at a small round café table with a laptop, surrounded by scattered paper documents and a coffee cup, his head resting in his hands in exasperation. The laptop screen glows with an ominous red error message interface. Through the café window behind him, the distinctive Singapore skyline with Marina Bay Sands is visible at dusk. The scene is rendered in warm vintage 1960s illustration style with muted oranges, teals, and cream colors, featuring slightly textured paper grain and soft halftone dot patterns. The composition emphasizes the contrast between the cozy café atmosphere and the technological frustration, with dramatic shadows cast by warm interior lighting mixing with the cool blue twilight outside.
